# 2️⃣ Vision Engine 설계

파일:

```
/vision/thumbnailAnalyzer.js
```

---

## 🎨 분석 항목

### 1. Brightness

```jsx
const mean = image.mean();
const brightness = mean.w / 255;
```

---

### 2. Contrast

```jsx
const gray = image.bgrToGray();
const { stddev } = gray.meanStdDev();
const contrast = stddev.at(0, 0) / 255;
```

---

### 3. Saturation

HSV 변환:

```jsx
const hsv = image.cvtColor(cv.COLOR_BGR2HSV);
```

S 채널 평균 사용.

---

### 4️⃣ 얼굴 감지 (핵심)

```jsx
const classifier = new cv.CascadeClassifier(cv.HAAR_FRONTALFACE_ALT2);
const grayImg = image.bgrToGray();
const { objects } = classifier.detectMultiScale(grayImg);
```

결과:

```jsx
faceCount = objects.length;
faceRatio = totalFaceArea / imageArea;
```

---

### 5️⃣ 엣지 밀도 (정보량)

```jsx
const edges = gray.canny(50, 150);
edgeDensity = edges.countNonZero() / imageArea;
```

